reviewText:
Exceptional Product, wonderful collection.  Bluray discs are flawless and play perfectly on my USA coded player.  Each movie in on it's own disc, so the movies are not compressed.  This is absolutely the best way to view these "lazy sunday" adventures.  Great stuff.

[Note:  This is the Australian version, but it's coded to the North America region and plays perfectly.  There are; however, NO subtitles].
The first DVD didn't work.  this was a gift and my kids were dissapointed.  They live in a different state than we do so its been hard to get it back to return it to you.
